commit.message:
Initialize SDL2 before loading cache file

Avoids issues with the locale being changed by the SDL2 initialization
while the json file is being loaded.

Use code suggested by HetorusNL

The code respects the uft-8 encoding more than my original.
add utf8 support
check if song text is no ascii
Changed the presets names in workflow
Fixed the presets for WSL2 Linxu

Add Linux preset for Visual Studio

Allows to work with wsl2 (for example ubuntu) in Visual Studio
Update actions for Node 20

adjustments to notelines.svg

fixes invisible note labels
makes the vertical line marking the current note to sing outlined so it's visible on any background

adjust lyrics highlight color, stroke opacity and width

change lyric text highlight color to the same as in the default theme
set stroke opacity for all lyrics texts to 1
set stroke width for all lyric texts to 1.5
Bump version to 1.3.1
